{"data":[{"date":"09:49 24/07","title":"Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Liverpool lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/liverpool-don-tin-du-tu-hang-thu-matip-chan-thuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 Joel Matip \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chia tay gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu ICC \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 trung t\u00e2m t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Dortmund.</h2><h2>Matip g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 Joel Matip \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb thay ra kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n ngay trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/video-tong-hop-liverpool-13-dortmund-icc-2018-329-191807.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Liverpool v\u00e0 Dortmund</span> cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua. HLV Jurgen Klopp lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 b\u1eafp \u0111\u00f9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Matip ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u01b0ng theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ch\u1ea9n \u0111o\u00e1n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ebft \u0111au kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf c\u01a1 kh\u00e1c. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u01a1 b\u1eafp. Hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ebft r\u00e1ch nh\u1ecf\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Klopp l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Matip\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Matip ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Liverpool lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Matip ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Liverpool lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/liverpool-don-tin-du-tu-hang-thu-matip-chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Matip ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Klopp t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Cameroon m\u1edbi g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Dortmund, Klopp v\u1eabn hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cJoel Matip s\u1ebd r\u1eddi tr\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Liverpool t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u01a1 m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Dortmund h\u00f4m Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 gi\u1eefa hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t v\u00e0 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay ra kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng n\u1eb1m \u1edf g\u1ea7n ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f9i m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 n\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u. D\u1eabu sao, Matip c\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u00ec v\u1eady, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Merseyside v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i Melwood\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Matip, Liverpool s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 2 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Van Dijk \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi l\u00e0 Joe Gomez v\u00e0 Ragnar Klavan. C\u1ea3 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t s\u1edbm m\u1ed9t chi\u1ec1u. V\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ebf, The Kop \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 ph\u00e1 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-danh-sach-7-cau-thu-giup-liverpool-thu-ve-100-trieu-bang-172-191890.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Danh s\u00e1ch 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00fap Liverpool thu v\u1ec1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhm-liverpool-dung-ky-vong-qua-nhieu-vao-alisson-172-191888.html\">NHM Liverpool \u0111\u1eebng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o Alisson</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1575","checkdouble":"191895"},{"date":"09:51 24/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh PAOK vs Basel 0h30 ng\u00e0y 25/7 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/nhan-dinh-paok-vs-basel-0h30-ngay-257-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PAOK vs Basel l\u00fac 0h30 ng\u00e0y 25/7 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19)): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh PAOK vs Basel 0h30 ng\u00e0y 257 Champions League 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh PAOK vs Basel 0h30 ng\u00e0y 257 Champions League 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/PAOK-vs-Basel.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">PAOK vs Basel</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>PAOK vs Basel: 2-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, PAOK c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean BXH gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG\u00a0Hy L\u1ea1p. V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y, PAOK gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 Champions League t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Basel, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eebng 20 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb c\u1eaft \u0111\u1ee9t m\u1ea1ch 8 m\u00f9a v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp khi c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 chung cu\u1ed9c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Young Boys t\u1edbi 15 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 sa s\u00fat tr\u1ea7m tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Basel.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Basel ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 th\u1ee5t l\u00f9i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Basel to\u00e0n thua 4 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2018/19. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, tr\u1eadn thua t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 St. Gallen, ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi Hy L\u1ea1p n\u00e0y, Basel ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 tr\u1eafng tay, b\u1edfi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1edb h\u00eanh v\u1edbi 13 b\u00e0n thua \u1edf 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3, d\u00f9 Basel kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n, b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y, PAOK nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nPAOK: P. Glykos, L\u00e9o Matos, S. Malezas, D. Chatziisaias, S. Kitsiou, Maur\u00edcio -O. El Kaddouri, G. Ktistopoulos, D. Limnios, G. Vrakas, I. Mystakidis.<br>\r\nBasel: J. Omlin, M. Such\u00fd, S. Widmer, \u00c9. \u00c1lvarez, E. C\u00fcmart, S. Di\u00e9, Z. Kuzmanovi\u0107, T. Xhaka, R. van Wolfswinkel, A. Kalulu, Albian Ajeti.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1574","checkdouble":"191896"},{"date":"10:15 24/07","title":"HLV Milan n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Bonucci c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sang M.U ho\u1eb7c Real?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/28/hlv-gattuso-muon-bonucci-o-lai-milan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, \"n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n\" trong pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p cho nhau.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p tr\u1eddi gi\u00e1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p tr\u1eddi gi\u00e1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Nan-nhan-cua-Sam-Ngoc-Duc-mong-muon-dieu-nay-sau-cu-dap-troi-gian-hinh-anh.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7\u00a0Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p tr\u1eddi gi\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a S\u1ea7m</em>\u00a0<em>Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c. \u1ea2nh: Zing.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai CLB TP.HCM v\u00e0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 22/7 t\u1edbi, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn. Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, c\u00f2n Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p b\u00ean ph\u00eda Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. Song Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng v\u1eabn hy v\u1ecdng Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft ti\u1ebft ch\u1ebf c\u1ea3m x\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef 'n\u1ed3i c\u01a1m' cho nhau.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh chia s\u1ebb: \"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng qua r\u1ed3i n\u00ean t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i may m\u1eafn khi kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb g\u00ec. Ch\u1ec9 mong Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c sau n\u00e0y \u0111\u1eebng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u00e1c \u00fd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u1eefa. \u0110\u00f4i ch\u00e2n gi\u00fap c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1m n\u00ean \u0111\u1eebng c\u1ed1 \u00fd tri\u1ec7t h\u1ea1 l\u1eabn nhau\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf sau pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a CLB TP.HCM b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t 15 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-nhieu-lan-roi-291-191892.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-nhieu-lan-roi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/vleague/sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-nhieu-lan-roi-291-191892.html\">S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chu-tich-huu-thang-noi-gi-khi-sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-168-191885.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/28/chu-tich-huu-thang-noi-gi-khi-sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chu-tich-huu-thang-noi-gi-khi-sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-168-191885.html\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o?</span><br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB TP.HCM Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1573","checkdouble":"191897"},{"date":"10:25 24/07","title":"Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/5/chelsea-chot-gia-ban-willian-cho-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca 3 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi mua Willian nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Sau khi Antoine Griezmann \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/Chelsea-ban-Willian-cho-Barca-voi-gia-70-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca 3 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi mua Willian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPhilippe Couttinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n Barca mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, HLV Ernesto Valverde c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-chuyen-nhuong/gui-de-nghi-lan-3-barca-quyet-mua-ngoi-sao-cua-chelsea-187-191704.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca \u0111\u00e3 3 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi mua Willian</span>. L\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng song \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Chelsea th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, sau \u0111\u00f3 Barca n\u00e2ng l\u00ean 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Barca g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 3 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, song Chelsea v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd. Theo Daily Mail, HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Willian v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Chelsea y\u00eau c\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u0103m nay s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 30, Barca s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea vs Crystal Palace Willian ghi ban\" title=\"Chelsea vs Crystal Palace Willian ghi ban\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/barca-nang-gia-hoi-mua-willian-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo The Sun, Chelsea ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Willian cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i bi\u00ean gi\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 M.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu Willian. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Willian cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u1edf l\u1ea1i thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i, b\u1edfi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 The Blues y\u00eau c\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Barca ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb b\u1ecf m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1572","checkdouble":"191898"},{"date":"10:24 24/07","title":"\"Liverpool v\u1eabn c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/liverpool-van-con-thieu-mot-tien-dao-dang-cap-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Harry Kewell kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n chi ti\u00eau \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Liverpool chi ti\u00eau m\u1ea1nh tay</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ea3ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n khi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh h\u1ea1ng n\u1eb7ng. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Naby Keita v\u00e0 Fabinho \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Anfield v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson c\u0169ng m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp The Kop</span> v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00e0 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ebf v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool Kewell khuy\u00ean The Kop mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool Kewell khuy\u00ean The Kop mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/liverpool-van-con-thieu-mot-tien-dao-dang-cap-the-gioi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool: Kewell khuy\u00ean Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n khi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean nh\u01b0 Mohamed Salah hay Virgil van Dijk \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 t\u1ed1t trong v\u00f2ng 12 th\u00e1ng qua. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Harry Kewell cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Merseyside v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean t\u1edd Daily Express, Kewell cho hay: \u201c\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cV\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Man City qu\u00e1 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt th\u00ec m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb lu m\u1edd. Nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Liverpool \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c. Ph\u00f2ng tr\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p m\u1ed9t trong ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u1eefa\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kewell k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o Liverpool m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 k\u00eau g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ea3ng b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0ng Kewell c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Liverpool. H\u1ecd v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u01b0 Alexander-Arnold v\u00e0 Andrew Robertson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMane, Salah v\u00e0 Firmino \u0111\u1ec1u thi \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Henderson \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u mong mu\u1ed1n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n theo tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-don-tin-du-tu-hang-thu-matip-chan-thuong-172-191895.html\">Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Liverpool lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-danh-sach-7-cau-thu-giup-liverpool-thu-ve-100-trieu-bang-172-191890.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Danh s\u00e1ch 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00fap Liverpool thu v\u1ec1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1571","checkdouble":"191900"},{"date":"10:03 24/07","title":"N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p tr\u1eddi gi\u00e1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/25/nan-nhan-cua-sam-ngoc-duc-mong-muon-dieu-nay-sau-cu-dap-troi-giang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, \"n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n\" trong pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p cho nhau.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p tr\u1eddi gi\u00e1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p tr\u1eddi gi\u00e1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Nan-nhan-cua-Sam-Ngoc-Duc-mong-muon-dieu-nay-sau-cu-dap-troi-gian-hinh-anh.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7\u00a0Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p tr\u1eddi gi\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a S\u1ea7m</em>\u00a0<em>Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c. \u1ea2nh: Zing.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai CLB TP.HCM v\u00e0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 22/7 t\u1edbi, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn. Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, c\u00f2n Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p b\u00ean ph\u00eda Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. Song Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng v\u1eabn hy v\u1ecdng Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft ti\u1ebft ch\u1ebf c\u1ea3m x\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef 'n\u1ed3i c\u01a1m' cho nhau.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh chia s\u1ebb: \"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng qua r\u1ed3i n\u00ean t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i may m\u1eafn khi kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb g\u00ec. Ch\u1ec9 mong Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c sau n\u00e0y \u0111\u1eebng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u00e1c \u00fd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u1eefa. \u0110\u00f4i ch\u00e2n gi\u00fap c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1m n\u00ean \u0111\u1eebng c\u1ed1 \u00fd tri\u1ec7t h\u1ea1 l\u1eabn nhau\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf sau pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a CLB TP.HCM b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t 15 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-nhieu-lan-roi-291-191892.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-nhieu-lan-roi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/vleague/sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-nhieu-lan-roi-291-191892.html\">S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chu-tich-huu-thang-noi-gi-khi-sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-168-191885.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/28/chu-tich-huu-thang-noi-gi-khi-sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chu-tich-huu-thang-noi-gi-khi-sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-168-191885.html\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o?</span><br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB TP.HCM Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1570","checkdouble":"191901"},{"date":"10:26 24/07","title":"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 24/7: Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Old Trafford","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/3/ngay-hom-nay-247.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (24/7). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)</div>\r\n<h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Old Trafford\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 247, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 247, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/chan-mu-pogba-co-dong-thai-san-sang-dau-quan-cho-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Marca loan tin s\u1ed1t d\u1ebbo, th\u00f4ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Mino Raiola, Paul Pogba th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o cho l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o MU bi\u1ebft, anh mu\u1ed1n chia tay Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng Cristiano Ronaldo, ch\u1ec9 sau 2 m\u00f9a c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPaul Pogba v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a h\u00e8 r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, khi c\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 nh\u01b0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn, Pogba v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Mourinho, s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 c\u0169 - m\u00e0 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n: nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf n\u00ean, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y tin \u0111\u1ed3n lan nhanh, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ph\u00e1p mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi MU \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A, Juventus - CLB m\u1edbi n\u1ed5 si\u00eau h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1m v\u1edbi Cristiano Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPogba \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 m\u00f9a \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f9ng Juventus, v\u1edbi 178 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh 4 Scudetto. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd anh mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh, thay v\u00ec trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Mourinho khi\u1ebfn Pogba c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ecb h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid quy\u1ebft l\u1eadp k\u1ec9 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Tottenham</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 Achraf Hakimi gia nh\u1eadp Dortmund theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 2 n\u0103m v\u00e0 mua Alvaro Odriozola t\u1eeb Real Sociedad, Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a y\u00ean t\u00e2m v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi \u201cl\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng\u201d Dani Carvajal \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Julen Lopetegui nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn cho \u201cK\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng\u201d l\u00e0 Kieran Trippier. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 d\u00f9 \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Croatia \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd The Sun, Real s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Spurs b\u00e1n Trippier. N\u1ebfu t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Bernabeu v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y, Trippier s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.</div>\r\n<h2>Barcelona \u0111\u1ea9y Douglas sang Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Sivasspor x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Douglas t\u1eeb Barcelona theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 8 tr\u1eadn ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp t\u1eeb khi \u201cG\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalunya\u201d mua anh v\u1ec1 Sao Paulo h\u00e8 2014 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 4 tri\u1ec7u euro (c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam 1,5 tri\u1ec7u euro ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Douglas b\u1ecb Barca l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u01b0a sang Sporting Gijon v\u00e0 Benfica \u0111\u1ec1u theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal s\u1eafp \u201ctr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n\u201d Iwobi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Theo t\u1edd Mirror, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb Lazio nh\u01b0ng Arsenal s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Alex Iwobi h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, \u201cPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7\u201d s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2022 v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nigeria khi anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 247 Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Old Trafford h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 247 Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Old Trafford h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/1/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-247-Tien-ve-Pogba-doi-roi-Old-Trafford-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Iwobi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Sturaro t\u1edbi Premier League</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Stefano Sturaro, \u00f4ng Carlo Volpi cho bi\u1ebft th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u CLB Anh, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 West Ham v\u00e0 Leicester. Sturaro \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh t\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi Juventus v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</div>\r\n<h2>Real tranh Telles v\u1edbi Juventus</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Theo Record (B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha), Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Alex Telles, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Juventus. Telles hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng l\u00e0 40 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u1edbi Porto.</div>\r\n<h2>Willian c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Barcelona d\u00e0nh cho Willian nh\u01b0ng Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Theo SunSport, The Blues ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil tr\u1eeb khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan ch\u1ecbu chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ngo\u00e0i Barca, Man Utd c\u0169ng \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e0y.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1569","checkdouble":"191902"},{"date":"11:40 24/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 khuy\u00ean Arsenal mua trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/10/27/juventus-41-sampdoria-cu-dup-bat-ngo-cua-trung-ve-chiellini.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ray Parlour cho r\u1eb1ng Arsenal th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 Chiellini s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong m\u01a1 d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</h2><h2>Parlour khuy\u00ean Arsenal mua Chiellini</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Unai Emery \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i Premier League. Nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi Stephan Lichtsteiner hay Sokratis Papastathopoulos \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Arsenal. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Bernd Leno c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef khung th\u00e0nh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ray Parlour cho r\u1eb1ng Arsenal v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Emery.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 khuy\u00ean Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Chiellini h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 khuy\u00ean Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Chiellini h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/10/27/juventus-41-sampdoria-cu-dup-bat-ngo-cua-trung-ve-chiellini.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Parlour khuy\u00ean Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Chiellini</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Sokratis l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1ed1t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Tony Adams ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSokratis c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb m\u1edd \u0111i \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ec9 huy \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Sokratis c\u0169ng c\u00f3 quen bi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Aubameyang v\u00e0 Mkhitaryan. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Arsenal v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00eam n\u1eefa, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 sau khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Sokratis v\u00e0 Lichtsteiner. H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 ra qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u01a1 h\u1edf \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cArsenal c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ee9ng m\u0169i ch\u1ecbu s\u00e0o v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Chiellini l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi Arsenal l\u00fac n\u00e0y\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Parlour khen ng\u1ee3i Lichtsteiner</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lichtsteiner hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc qua tu\u1ed5i 34. Nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u00ean gia v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cBellerin s\u1ebd h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb Lichtsteiner, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Bellerin t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t hay nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra khi Lichtsteiner h\u00e9t v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t c\u1eadu \u1ea5y trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cLichtsteiner s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng sau nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf Juventus c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ea3 trong l\u1eabn ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 Arsenal c\u1ea7n b\u1ea5y l\u00e2u nay\u201d.<br>\r\n</em><br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-arsenal-ung-ho-tien-ve-mesut-ozil-chia-tay-doi-tuyen-duc-184-191865.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Arsenal \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/soc-arsenal-lai-muon-mua-them-mot-thu-mon-nua-tu-bundesliga-172-191764.html\">S\u1ed1c: Arsenal l\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1eefa t\u1eeb Bundesliga</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1568","checkdouble":"191903"},{"date":"11:22 24/07","title":"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Sturridge \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/goc-nhin-sturridge-o-lai-liverpool-la-dieu-tot-cho-tat-ca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi t\u1ea1i sao Daniel Sturridge \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a r\u1eddi Liverpool sau su\u1ed1t 4 m\u00f9a \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn theo \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a \u0111en. M\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t cho vi\u1ec7c Sturridge \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chu\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y cay \u0111\u1eafng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGia nh\u1eadp Liverpool \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2013 t\u1eeb Chelsea, Daniel Sturridge l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u00f5 n\u00e9t. Ngay tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft v\u1edbi Mansfield Town \u1edf v\u00f2ng 3 c\u00fap FA 4 ng\u00e0y sau, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho The Kop ch\u1ec9 sau 7 ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t, m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a h\u1ebft, 2 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1i Premier League, Sturridge c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u &ldquo;n\u1ed5 s\u00fang&rdquo;. Anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Liverpool \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n trong c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kho\u00e1c \u00e1o sau Ray Kennedy n\u0103m 1974. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 cho t\u1edbi h\u1ebft m\u00f9a 2012/13, &ldquo;Studger&rdquo; ghi t\u1edbi 11 b\u00e0n sau 16 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea3 Man United, Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Sturridge \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Sturridge \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Goc-nhin-Sturridge-o-lai-Liverpool-la-dieu-tot-cho-tat-ca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sturridge t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng khi m\u1edbi t\u1edbi Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 Sturridge c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Liverpool b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Luis Suarez. H\u1ecd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh kh\u1ea9u &ldquo;\u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e1c hai n\u00f2ng&rdquo;, gi\u00fap L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf su\u00fdt l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Cho t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 36, Liverpool v\u1eabn c\u00f2n d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea, n\u01a1i Steven Gerrard c\u00f3 c\u00fa tr\u01b0\u1ee3t ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Crystal Palace 3-3 d\u00f9 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-0 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Liverpool v\u00e0 Sturridge \u00f4m h\u1eadn. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i c\u00fap b\u1ea1c Premier League theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i n\u1ed5i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, 1 n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ee7a Sturridge t\u1ea1i Liverpool v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. T\u00ednh ra, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh t\u1ea1i Birmingham ghi t\u1edbi 35 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho The Kop ch\u1ec9 sau 49 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. H\u00ecnh b\u00f3ng v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a s\u00e2n Anfield v\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edd m\u1edd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sturridge chan thuong\" title=\"Sturridge chan thuong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Sturridge-chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p anh ch\u1eefng l\u1ea1i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1. Sturridge b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 bao nhi\u00eau trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec l\u1ee5i t\u00e0n b\u1ea5y nhi\u00eau trong 4 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. N\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111eo b\u00e1m anh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u1eadn t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng, Sturridge \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 12 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e0i ng\u1eafn c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 trong 4 n\u0103m qua. N\u00e0o l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f9i, g\u00e2n khoeo, h\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i, b\u1eafp ch\u00e2n&hellip;, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn m\u0169i c\u00f4ng t\u1eebng khuynh \u0111\u1ea3o Premier League ch\u00ecm trong \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c l\u1eabn t\u00e2m h\u1ed3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Liverpool, gi\u1edd Sturridge trong m\u1eaft nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec &ldquo;h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i&rdquo;. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Roberto Firmino b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u1ebb gi\u00e0u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-tiet-lo-su-thuc-dau-long-tu-sturridge-172-189649.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/10/liverpool-tiet-lo-su-thuc-dau-long-tu-sturridge.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-tiet-lo-su-thuc-dau-long-tu-sturridge-172-189649.html\">Liverpool ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c \u0111au l\u00f2ng t\u1eeb Sturridge</span><br>\r\n<span>Liverpool b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o h\u1ecfi mua ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn h\u1eefu d\u1ee5ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn Sturridge kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u cho West Brom khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf n\u1eeda sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18. \u0110i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Sturridge \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool c\u0169ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u1edf 5 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t cho Liverpool (\u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 1 hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ea1i), Sturridge \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sturridge choi tot tai Liverpool\" title=\"Sturridge choi tot tai Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Sturridge-choi-tot-tai-Liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sturridge ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a 2018/19</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u0169i \u0111inh ba Mane, Firmino v\u00e0 Salah \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Sturridge n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Khi \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn ra r\u1eb1ng ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb b\u1ed9 ba h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t tr\u00ean, nh\u1eefng &ldquo;ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba&rdquo; nh\u01b0 Ings, Origi, Markovic hay nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Woodburn, Solanke \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eb1ng Studger.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, C\u0110V c\u1ee7a Liverpool d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi Sturridge. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 tr\u00ean h\u1ebft l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ebd tr\u00f2n 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 9 t\u1edbi v\u1eabn ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 63 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 133 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua cho The Kop (trung b\u00ecnh (0.47 b\u00e0n/ tr\u1eadn).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sturridge can thiet cho Liverpool\" title=\"Sturridge can thiet cho Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Sturridge-can-thiet-cho-Liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sturridge v\u1eabn h\u1eefu \u00edch cho Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e3y l\u01b0u \u00fd: Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb Salah, nh\u1eefng Mane (0.45 b\u00e0n/ tr\u1eadn) v\u00e0 Firmino (0.35 b\u00e0n/ tr\u1eadn) \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t l\u00e0m b\u00e0n cao nh\u01b0 Sturridge. L\u1eadt l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Liverpool c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf c\u00f3 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh t\u1eeb Chelsea n\u0103m 2013. Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu Sturridge kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng? Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i Liverpool v\u00e0 \u0110T Anh. Nh\u01b0ng ngay c\u1ea3 l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y, khi b\u1ecb v\u00ed nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t &ldquo;th\u01b0\u01a1ng binh&rdquo;, Sturridge v\u1eabn h\u1eefu \u00edch cho L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-bat-ngo-dam-bao-tuong-lai-cho-phe-pham-cua-liverpool-172-191866.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/klopp-bat-ngo-dam-bao-tuong-lai-cho-phe-pham-cua-liverpool.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-bat-ngo-dam-bao-tuong-lai-cho-phe-pham-cua-liverpool-172-191866.html\">Klopp b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai cho &ldquo;ph\u1ebf ph\u1ea9m&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span><br>\r\n<span>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng Daniel Sturridge \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf l\u1ea1i Anfield khi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Liverpool.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Jurgen Klopp c\u0169ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t Sturridge trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng. Vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1eebng 26 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T Anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Merseyside mang nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Sturridge, n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Liverpool, anh ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trung b\u00ecnh v\u00e0 nh\u1ecf. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n Sturridge \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ph\u1ea3i tranh ch\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i ch\u00fat n\u00e0o v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n s\u1eed ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a anh. Ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 29, vi\u1ec7c sang M\u1ef9 hay ch\u00e2u \u00c1 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sturridge va Klopp\" title=\"Sturridge va Klopp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Sturridge-va-Klopp.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Klopp mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Anfield</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, Liverpool c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n Sturridge \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Nh\u1eefng Mane, Firmino v\u00e0 Salah v\u1eabn chi\u1ebfm su\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh The Kop, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i nghi ng\u1edd. Song Sturridge s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i cho h\u1ecd m\u1ed7i khi c\u1ea7n k\u00edp. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng Sturridge v\u00e0 k\u00e9m xa b\u1ed9 ba MFS. S\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fac Liverpool c\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd mong ch\u1edd s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn t\u1edbi t\u1eeb s\u1ed1 15 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Sturridge qua tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u1ee7a Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc Blackburn (Giao h\u1eefu)</strong>:\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/20/Blackburn-Rovers-vs-Liverpool.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-don-tin-du-tu-hang-thu-matip-chan-thuong-172-191895.html\">Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Liverpool lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-van-con-thieu-mot-tien-dao-dang-cap-the-gioi-172-191900.html\">Liverpool v\u1eabn c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-danh-sach-7-cau-thu-giup-liverpool-thu-ve-100-trieu-bang-172-191890.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Danh s\u00e1ch 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00fap Liverpool thu v\u1ec1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhm-liverpool-dung-ky-vong-qua-nhieu-vao-alisson-172-191888.html\">NHM Liverpool \u0111\u1eebng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o Alisson</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-nam-nay-se-la-nam-cua-chung-toi-172-191880.html\">Klopp: &ldquo;N\u0103m nay s\u1ebd l\u00e0 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1567","checkdouble":"191904"},{"date":"11:36 24/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Astana vs Midtjylland 21h00 ng\u00e0y 24/7 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/24/nhan-dinh-astana-vs-midtjylland-21h00-ngay-247-champions-league-201819.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Astana vs Midtjylland l\u00fac 21h00 ng\u00e0y 24/7 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19)): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Astana vs Midtjylland 21h00 ng\u00e0y 247 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Astana vs Midtjylland 21h00 ng\u00e0y 247 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Astana-vs-Midtjylland.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Astana vs Midtjylland</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Astana vs Midtjylland: 1-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Kazakhstan, Astana \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9c t\u00f4n khi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2018. Ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee9 5 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 m\u00e0 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi tay h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u0103ng hoa \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i, Astana c\u0169ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn Champions League 2018/18, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u1ecd tham d\u1ef1 t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Sutjeska, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u00ean t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Montenegro sau c\u1ea3 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn (1-0, 2-0) \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Midtjylland \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u01b0\u1ee3t qu\u00e1 s\u1ef1 mong \u0111\u1ee3i b\u1edfi th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh. B\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Midtjylland \u0111ang tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng (3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, 2 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi Kazakhstan \u0111\u00eam nay. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nAstana: Muzhikov \u2013 Kleinheisler \u2013 Despotovic \u2013 Murtazaev \u2013 Eric \u2013 Rukavina \u2013 Anicic \u2013 Shomko \u2013 Postnikov \u2013 Tomasov \u2013 Maevski<br>\r\nMidtjylland: Wikheim \u2013 Duelund \u2013 Onuachu \u2013 Hansen \u2013 Sviatchenko \u2013 Hende \u2013 Sanneh \u2013 Munksgaard \u2013 Nicolaisen \u2013 Poulsen \u2013 Sparv</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1566","checkdouble":"191905"},{"date":"07:12 24/07","title":"Barca l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang M\u1ef9, Messi v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/barca-len-duong-sang-my-messi-vang-mat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Messi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Barca.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMessi v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, El Pulga v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ngh\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean danh s\u00e1ch sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 h\u1ecd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7c c\u00e1ch mi\u1ec5n tham d\u1ef1 tour n\u00e0y, trong \u0111\u00f3 bao g\u1ed3m Luis Suarez, Philippe Coutinho v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u01b0 Gerard Pique, Sergio Busquets v\u00e0 Jordi Alba. Nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 Samuel Umtiti, Ousmane Dembele (Ph\u00e1p), Ivan Rakitic (Croatia) th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 x\u1ea3 h\u01a1i \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Barca tham d\u1ef1 du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Messi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Barca tham d\u1ef1 du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/Messi-khong-co-mat-trong-doi-hinh-cua-Barca-tham-du-du-dau-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Barca sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nV\u00e0o h\u00f4m nay, Barca \u0111\u00e3 bay \u0111\u1ebfn Portland, Oregon \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh c\u1ee7a Nike. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ernesto Valverde s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Tottenham t\u1ea1i Los Angeles v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y, sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 g\u1eb7p AS Roma t\u1ea1i Dallas v\u00e0 AC Milan \u1edf Santa Clara. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quay v\u1ec1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho La Liga.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tour du \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Valverde xem gi\u00f2 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh h\u1ecd m\u1edbi \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u01b0 Arthur Melo v\u00e0 Clement Lenglet. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch nguy hi\u1ec3m g\u1ed3m Andre Gomes, Lucas Digne v\u00e0 Rafinha c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 13 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i B c\u0169ng tham gia c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi HLV Valverde, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9, s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn khi Messi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/bar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Danh s\u00e1ch h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Barca tham d\u1ef1 tour du \u0111\u1ea5u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-cua-barca-tho-phao-vi-khong-con-phai-so-messi-180-191789.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/tan-binh-cua-barca-tho-phao-vi-khong-con-phai-so-messi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-cua-barca-tho-phao-vi-khong-con-phai-so-messi-180-191789.html\">T\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Barca th\u1edf ph\u00e0o v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee3 Messi</span><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp Barca t\u1eeb Sevilla, Clement Lenglet chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Messi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/gui-de-nghi-lan-3-barca-quyet-mua-ngoi-sao-cua-chelsea-187-191704.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/gui-de-nghi-lan-3-barca-quyet-mua-ngoi-sao-cua-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/gui-de-nghi-lan-3-barca-quyet-mua-ngoi-sao-cua-chelsea-187-191704.html\">G\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u1ea7n 3, Barca quy\u1ebft mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh, CLB Barcelona v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 ba \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Willian t\u1eeb Chelsea.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1565","checkdouble":"191877"},{"date":"07:27 24/07","title":"Xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00e0n \u201cc\u01b0\u1edbp d\u00e2u\u201d th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Malcolm","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/xuat-hien-dien-bien-khong-tuong-man-cuop-dau-thuong-vu-malcolm.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i v\u1edbi scandal l\u1edbn, B\u00f2 t\u00f3t \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay t\u01b0\u1edbng. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o David Villa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Luis Enrique \u0111em l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho \u0110T.</h2><h2><br>\r\nVilla mu\u1ed1n T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra 1 ng\u00e0y, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Fernando Hierro thay th\u1ebf. Sau gi\u1ea3i, Hierro c\u0169ng r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Luis Enrique &ndash; c\u1ef1u HLV c\u1ee7a Barca, v\u00e0 t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u La Liga khi c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecf qua s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, B\u00f2 t\u00f3t c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch EURO 2020. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u David Villa \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Enrique: &ldquo;Th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t ra cho \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, b\u1edfi \u0110T \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u trong nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Villa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Luis Enrique\" title=\"HLV Luis Enrique\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/1/23/dai-thang-eibar-hlv-enrique-van-chua-hai-long.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>David Villa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Luis Enrique</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, v\u00ec v\u1eady th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn m\u1eaft ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0m \u0111\u00fang, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t, b\u1ea1n th\u1eafng. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 v\u1eady.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0110T Nga c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do h\u1ecd ti\u1ec5n T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 di\u1ec5n ra, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 EURO 2020, v\u00ec v\u1eady \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u1eafp r\u00e1p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao nh\u1ea5t, sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. D\u00f9 sao v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha&rdquo; &ndash; David Villa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Luis Enrique.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/luis-enrique-tu-tin-tai-thiet-tay-ban-nha-184-191508.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/luis-enrique-tu-tin-tai-thiet-tay-ban-nha.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/luis-enrique-tu-tin-tai-thiet-tay-ban-nha-184-191508.html\">Luis Enrique t\u1ef1 tin t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span><br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV 48 tu\u1ed5i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ldbd-tay-ban-nha-nai-ni-pique-dung-chia-tay-dtqg-421-190823.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/ldbd-tay-ban-nha-nai-ni-pique-dung-chia-tay-dtqg.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ldbd-tay-ban-nha-nai-ni-pique-dung-chia-tay-dtqg-421-190823.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u00e0i n\u1ec9 Pique \u0111\u1eebng chia tay \u0110TQG</span><br>\r\nGerard Pique chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, song L\u0110B\u0110 x\u1ee9 s\u1edf B\u00f2 t\u00f3t mu\u1ed1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Barca thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1564","checkdouble":"191878"},{"date":"07:50 24/07","title":"Ozil ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1eeb tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/ozil-tiep-tuc-bi-danh-hoi-dong-tu-tuyen-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Lothar Matthaus ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mesut Ozil sau quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia, v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 anh quay l\u1ea1i m\u00e0u \u00e1o n\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nOzil b\u1ecb huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u00ea tr\u00e1ch t\u1eeb Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Bayern (Uli Hoeness) r\u1eb1ng&hellip; &ldquo;<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ozil-chia-tay-tuyen-duc-chu-tich-bayern-ha-he-mat-sat-184-191852.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ozil \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 c*t trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua</span>&rdquo;, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n n\u00e9m \u0111\u00e1. V\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Lothar Matthaus l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb&rdquo; &ndash; Matthaus cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;Mesut \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, nh\u01b0ng kho\u1ea3ng 1 n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i qua c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch l\u00ean ng\u00f4i World Cup 2014.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh hay th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn Mesut Ozil d\u01b0\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, v\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00ea th\u1ea3m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lothar Matthaus ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mesut Ozil th\u1eadm t\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lothar Matthaus ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mesut Ozil th\u1eadm t\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Lothar-Matthaus-chi-trich-Mesut-Ozil-tham-te-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lothar Matthaus ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mesut Ozil th\u1eadm t\u1ec7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay th\u1ebf nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9. \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c b\u1edfi Mexico v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Ozil. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra trong 2 n\u0103m qua.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 Ozil kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap cho \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c n\u1eefa. Gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. V\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c, tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n m\u1edf c\u1eeda ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 t\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c. Mesut Ozil \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0110T 10 n\u0103m qua, Sami Khedira, Jerome Boateng hay Serge Gnabry c\u0169ng v\u1eady.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec c\u1ea3. <strong>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y&rdquo;</strong> &ndash; Lothar Matthaus ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mesut Ozil.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ldbd-duc-phan-phao-ozil-sau-cao-buoc-phan-biet-chung-toc-184-191871.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/ldbd-duc-phan-phao-ozil-sau-cao-buoc-phan-biet-chung-toc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ldbd-duc-phan-phao-ozil-sau-cao-buoc-phan-biet-chung-toc-184-191871.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o Ozil sau c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c</span><br>\r\nL\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Mesut Ozil, sau khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ozil-chia-tay-tuyen-duc-chu-tich-bayern-ha-he-mat-sat-184-191852.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/ozil-chia-tay-tuyen-duc-chu-tich-bayern-ha-he-mat-sat.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ozil-chia-tay-tuyen-duc-chu-tich-bayern-ha-he-mat-sat-184-191852.html\">Ozil chia tay tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bayern h\u1ea3 h\u00ea m\u1ea1t s\u00e1t</span><br>\r\nUli Hoeness vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed x\u00fac ph\u1ea1m th\u1eb3ng m\u1eb7t ng\u00f4i sao Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/tam-thu-cua-mesut-ozil-giot-nuoc-tran-ly-389-191838.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/tam-thu-cua-mesut-ozil-giot-nuoc-tran-ly.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/tam-thu-cua-mesut-ozil-giot-nuoc-tran-ly-389-191838.html\">T\u00e2m th\u01b0 c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil: Gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00e0n ly</span><br>\r\nSau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c, Mesut Ozil l\u00e0 t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh anh v\u00e0 Gundogan ch\u1ee5p c\u00f9ng T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3. Ozil \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1563","checkdouble":"191879"},{"date":"08:01 24/07","title":"Klopp: \u201cN\u0103m nay s\u1ebd l\u00e0 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/klopp-nam-nay-se-la-nam-cua-chung-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em v\u1ec1, HLV Jurgen Klopp t\u1ef1 tin gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng Liverpool.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nThe Kop \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 t\u00e2n binh Naby Keita, Fabinho, Xherdan Shaqiri v\u00e0 Alisson \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em v\u1ec1 Anfield v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League sau bao n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, HLV Jurgen Klopp th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn: &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, nh\u01b0ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc \u1edf m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp t\u1ef1 tin gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng Liverpool m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Klopp t\u1ef1 tin gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng Liverpool m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/klopp.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jurgen Klopp t\u1ef1 tin gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ec1 y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n \u0111\u00e2u.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Man City kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o, v\u00ec v\u1eady ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam Mahrez. Man United c\u0169ng v\u1eady, \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong \u0111\u1ee3i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho danh hi\u1ec7u, m\u1ecdi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00fap.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3 v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn 100 s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng v\u1eady, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t, c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1i k\u1ebft t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p&rdquo; &ndash; Klopp t\u1ef1 tin gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng Liverpool.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/karius-thua-nhan-tuong-lai-bat-dinh-sau-khi-liverpool-don-alisson-172-191863.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/karius-thua-nhan-tuong-lai-bat-dinh-sau-khi-liverpool-don-alisson.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/karius-thua-nhan-tuong-lai-bat-dinh-sau-khi-liverpool-don-alisson-172-191863.html\">Karius th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh sau khi Liverpool \u0111\u00f3n Alisson</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t trong khung g\u1ed7 Anfield \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ra \u0111i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-bat-ngo-dam-bao-tuong-lai-cho-phe-pham-cua-liverpool-172-191866.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/klopp-bat-ngo-dam-bao-tuong-lai-cho-phe-pham-cua-liverpool.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-bat-ngo-dam-bao-tuong-lai-cho-phe-pham-cua-liverpool-172-191866.html\">Klopp b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai cho &ldquo;ph\u1ebf ph\u1ea9m&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng Daniel Sturridge \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf l\u1ea1i Anfield khi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Liverpool.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1562","checkdouble":"191880"},{"date":"08:18 24/07","title":"Enrique c\u1ea7n gi\u00fap \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch EURO 2020","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/enrique-can-giup-dt-tay-ban-nha-vo-dich-euro-2020.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i v\u1edbi scandal l\u1edbn, B\u00f2 t\u00f3t \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay t\u01b0\u1edbng. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o David Villa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Luis Enrique \u0111em l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho \u0110T.</h2><h2><br>\r\nVilla mu\u1ed1n T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra 1 ng\u00e0y, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Fernando Hierro thay th\u1ebf. Sau gi\u1ea3i, Hierro c\u0169ng r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Luis Enrique &ndash; c\u1ef1u HLV c\u1ee7a Barca, v\u00e0 t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u La Liga khi c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecf qua s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, B\u00f2 t\u00f3t c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch EURO 2020. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u David Villa \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Enrique: &ldquo;Th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t ra cho \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, b\u1edfi \u0110T \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u trong nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Villa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Luis Enrique\" title=\"HLV Luis Enrique\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/1/23/dai-thang-eibar-hlv-enrique-van-chua-hai-long.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>David Villa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Luis Enrique</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, v\u00ec v\u1eady th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn m\u1eaft ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0m \u0111\u00fang, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t, b\u1ea1n th\u1eafng. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 v\u1eady.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0110T Nga c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do h\u1ecd ti\u1ec5n T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 di\u1ec5n ra, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 EURO 2020, v\u00ec v\u1eady \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u1eafp r\u00e1p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao nh\u1ea5t, sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. D\u00f9 sao v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha&rdquo; &ndash; David Villa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Luis Enrique.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/luis-enrique-tu-tin-tai-thiet-tay-ban-nha-184-191508.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/luis-enrique-tu-tin-tai-thiet-tay-ban-nha.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/luis-enrique-tu-tin-tai-thiet-tay-ban-nha-184-191508.html\">Luis Enrique t\u1ef1 tin t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span><br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV 48 tu\u1ed5i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ldbd-tay-ban-nha-nai-ni-pique-dung-chia-tay-dtqg-421-190823.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/ldbd-tay-ban-nha-nai-ni-pique-dung-chia-tay-dtqg.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ldbd-tay-ban-nha-nai-ni-pique-dung-chia-tay-dtqg-421-190823.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u00e0i n\u1ec9 Pique \u0111\u1eebng chia tay \u0110TQG</span><br>\r\nGerard Pique chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, song L\u0110B\u0110 x\u1ee9 s\u1edf B\u00f2 t\u00f3t mu\u1ed1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Barca thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1561","checkdouble":"191881"}]}